node.text:
When I first discovered The Secret, I knew for sure that it was the truth for our life on planet Earth. But I also knew that there must be even more truth to discover, and so I became the most diligent seeker. I studied every philosophy and spiritual tradition I could lay my hands on, from thousands of years ago, right through to the great teachers alive today. That’s how a great part of my journey from The Secret to The Greatest Secret was spent scouring the archives of Conscious TV, a wonderful and totally free online resource featuring interviews with many of the great enlightened beings of our time. And so, you can imagine how thrilled I was to be interviewed recently by Iain McNay for Conscious TV. I am delighted to present this interview, and I hope you enjoy our conversation – “Finding The Greatest Secret.” Watch the whole interview here: https://visit.thesecret.tv/RB-IV-IMc

"What a full circle! I watched and read @thesecret365 when I was disabled in bed. ⁠

I was broke. ⁠
⁠

⁠
Fast forward a few years after making it part of my life and I got a dm from the creators wanting to send me their newest book!!! How freaking COOL is that!!! It worked so well, I grew a massive audience and got to help them promote the newest instalment! ⁠
⁠
#TheGreatestSecret is available now online and in bookstores. Trust me… life can be fun, and magical, and happy… if you let it be 😉🤫⁠
#GOTEAM"
